{"tid":210390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【嘔番七張機出黎】吳克儉外訪飛行里數夠換七機票","createTime":"2017-04-21T01:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T01:40:05.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"889b6a1901eaca18f3a5761b1995dd235fd36ab4","tid":210390,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:30:50.000Z","msg":"即時新聞港聞 選擇分類 <br />\n吳克儉外訪飛行里數夠換七機票<br />\n2017-04-21 06:26 文字大小<br />\n吳克儉外訪飛行里數夠換七機票。資料圖片<br />\n1/1吳克儉外訪飛行里數夠換七機票。資料圖片<br />\n教育局局長吳克儉因頻頻外訪備受批評，據立法會財委會的文件透露，過去五個財政年度，他因公幹旅程所得的飛行里數逾二十一萬六千，足夠兌換七張香港來回東京的經濟客位機票。但吳克儉自上任以從未兌換任何已賺取的飛行里數。<br />\n<br />\n而吳克儉昨日已離港出訪上海杭州，昨午更與上海市教育委員會副主任丁曉東會面，商議加強兩地教育的合作機會，特別是高等院校方面。明日探訪浙江大學，出席該校與本港理工大學合辦的「一帶一路」創新創業國際高峰論壇。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/886977/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F886977%2F&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=53345ccb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F886977%2F&h=586e1225\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/886977/</a>"},{"pid":"1b6b0eb600131e63a2ac76117e84e3436b6c63dd","tid":210390,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:32:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c0813eaca998750b0cca539a2afddb0e39099c2f","tid":210390,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:34:07.000Z","msg":"祝佢一家團聚咪算囉<br />\n利申:積緊口德<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86a4b10039f5518bc417c3b00c06ae1a25abe8a","tid":210390,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T01:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>祝佢一家團聚咪算囉<br />\n利申:積緊口德<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔得 佢開公數架 ！<br />\n條死廢坑摶大霧呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c208c4e441bc510ec32